Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,THE COLLABORATIVE RAIDEN
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.64,0:02:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, now, little girl.\NI wouldn't struggle if I were you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.27,0:02:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Underground Palace\Nof the Undead Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading for the entrance\Ndown an extinct volcano.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.24,0:02:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One wrong move and down you go\Ninto the abyss.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,We've imprisoned the girl in a cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.33,0:02:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,And a message just arrived from a Heyedra.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.46,0:02:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra, the Dark Commander,\Nwill be here shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.75,0:02:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hadorra?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,My name is Baduck.\NI'm a swordsman for Princess Leona.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.01,0:02:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,For Leona?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm just\Na wandering soldier for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Is Princess Leona safe?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.81,0:02:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Princess always said,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.82,0:02:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,"We can win once Dai comes.\NEveryone hold out until then!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.95,0:03:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.24,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So where's the Princess now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.33,0:03:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I was separated from everybody when\Nthe Undead Legion destroyed the temple.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.67,0:03:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But, the three most powerful Sages\Nin Papunica are always with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.38,0:03:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure they're alive\Nout there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.01,0:03:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We got split up with Gomechan,\Nso I guess it's just us now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.48,0:03:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That old man's going to be disappointed\Nwhen he hears Hyunckel kicked our butts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.90,0:03:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you use\Nthe power of your mark back there?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:49.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Listening to Hyunckel,\NI understood how he felt.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.91,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You understood?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.75,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was raised by monsters, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.08,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If somebody ever killed Grampa Burasu,\NI'd probably hate them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.55,0:04:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't get mad\Nwhen I thought about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.76,0:04:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You moron! If we don't beat him,\Nwe can't save Maam or the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We fight! Once more, together!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.15,0:04:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The Underground Palace.\NIt's been 15 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.82,0:04:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So this place used to be your home castle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.90,0:04:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.78,0:04:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, Sir Dark Commander.\NI see you're doing quite well.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,To what do I owe this visit?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.21,0:04:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Call it a battlefield inspection.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.92,0:04:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I know the Dark King ordered you\Nto kill Dai, but I had my concerns.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Your concerns are unnecessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.05,0:04:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already fought him. He was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.73,0:04:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, I'll kill him for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.35,0:04:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Strength-wise, an obvious result.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,However, you're a human,\Nand a former student of Aban.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Flazzard voiced his doubts\Nthat you might somehow fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.16,0:05:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just let the stupid general whine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.46,0:05:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen! My orders come directly\Nfrom Ban, the Dark King, himself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.05,0:05:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No one, no matter who, may question them!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.47,0:05:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Has Crocodine shown up recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.89,0:05:39.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He left his tank of Resurrection Fluid\Nbefore he was fully healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.06,0:05:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought he might have gone after Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't seen him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.78,0:05:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stay a while\Nand look around?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.99,0:05:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Revel in the memories\Nof the rise and fall of an empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.08,0:05:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Dark Commander." Hah!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you'd been strong enough,\Nmy father wouldn't have died.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just wait and I'll show you\Njust how weak you really are.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.51,0:06:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That insolent brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.47,0:06:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What does Dark King Ban even see in him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps he picked him on whim.\NOr perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was back when Dark King Ban\Nchose the Six Legion Commanders.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My Dark King, I cannot agree\Nwith making Hyunckel a Legion Commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.54,0:06:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He is a human! And a student of Aban!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.50,0:06:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel learned from Aban\Nin order to kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.29,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite audacious, wouldn't you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.26,0:06:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, should something happen to\Nmy power, the Undead Legion will suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.18,0:06:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,A living human is the best candidate\Nto comfortably control the Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.31,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you favor him so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.23,0:07:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,His eyes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.02,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Those eyes are magnificent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eyes that curse all around them\Nand burn with aggravated rage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.86,0:07:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,They are what I seek.\NTruly the eyes of an Underworld warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.71,0:07:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dark King Ban is great,\Nbut his motives can be unfathomable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.55,0:07:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Regardless, if Dai is killed, so be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:36.22,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hyunckel fails,\Nit gives us reason to punish him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:39.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, good morning, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.31,0:07:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.10,0:07:49.03,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my old Chain Mail,\Nbut it's still usable.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, have you seen Popp anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.45,0:07:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? I saw him in the forest earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:08:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.\NHe never wakes up before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.51,0:08:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.60,0:08:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.01,0:08:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like?\NI just bound with a new spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.81,0:08:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A new spell?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.31,0:08:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't beat him by sword.\NSo we'll have to beat him by magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.65,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you forget? His armour repels magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, you know the Weather-type spell,\NRana, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.37,0:08:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, wait, what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.74,0:08:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I just bound with the spell that\Nsummons lightning clouds, Ranarion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.96,0:08:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the most basic\Nof the spells that control weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:09:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking all night\Nfor a spell that might work on Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.39,0:09:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,And I found one! An attack spell\Nthat's guaranteed to hurt him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.56,0:09:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Raiden!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.23,0:09:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Raiden?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.40,0:09:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,His armour repels all spells,\Nbut it still has to be made of metal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.53,0:09:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That means, the shock\Nfrom a Electric-type spell
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.58,0:09:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,should penetrate his armour\Nand damage him directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.29,0:09:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But Raiden is a spell only a Hero can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.75,0:09:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use it, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.67,0:09:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we do it together!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.84,0:09:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.51,0:09:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Raiden summons lightning clouds\Nand strikes enemies with lightning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.26,0:09:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So if I summon the clouds with my spell,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,even your Magic Power should be enough\Nto drop a lightning bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.19,0:09:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.86,0:09:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We combine our spells,\Ndefeat him, and save Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.74,0:10:01.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Let's try it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirits scattered in the heavens,\Nhear my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.71,0:10:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Ranarion!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.18,0:10:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe this spell\Nwas a little too advanced for me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.11,0:10:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Do it, Dai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.95,0:10:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked! I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.79,0:10:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You dummy! Look closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.79,0:10:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.25,0:10:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already got the clouds,\Nso of course it worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the point if you miss?!\NDo it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Open it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.18,0:11:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NYou're just bait to lure in Dai.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I'm finished, you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.77,0:11:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You won't kill me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't kill a girl.\NEven if she's an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.45,0:11:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the basic code of a warrior\Nmy father taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.45,0:11:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was the model warrior.\NI still believe that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.38,0:11:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You respected your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.92,0:11:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:42.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why you hate Master Aban\Nfor taking his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.93,0:11:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.76,0:11:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I forgive Aban for killing him\Nfor that justice and peace nonsense?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.56,0:11:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel, you poor soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.73,0:12:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Your pain of losing your father\Nwas so great, you had to blame someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But that doesn't mean\Nyou should hate justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That wouldn't make your father happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.20,0:12:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in the Dark Army, but your father\Nwas a good, honorable man, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.59,0:12:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.05,0:12:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Open your eyes, Hyunckel!\NYou're a better man than that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a weakling who would vent\Nhis anger on others out of sorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.52,0:12:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.28,0:12:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.04,0:12:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Those kids have been going at it\Nfor half a day. Just how tough are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, a little more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.34,0:13:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.55,0:13:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! You're starting to hit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.97,0:13:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I struck a defenseless girl.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.47,0:13:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But, when I look into her eyes,\NI find I can't rebut her.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.44,0:13:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem quite taken by that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.16,0:13:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,With one spell,\NI could make her fall in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be strong,\Nbut you lack experience in...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.58,0:13:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.04,0:13:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You parasite!\NYou shame of the Six Legion Commanders!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.71,0:13:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Begone from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.42,0:13:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.22,0:13:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodine lost because\Nhe didn't listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.89,0:13:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet he lost because\Nyou put stupid ideas in his head!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I no longer have ears for anyone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will fight as I see fit!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.62,0:14:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Good! One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.29,0:14:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.89,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, this is good!\NNow we can go save Maam!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.89,0:14:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.52,0:14:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Come on, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:50.57,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BAGIKUROSAI{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}\NVORTEX-TYPE SPELL
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:55.58,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}BLOODY SUKURAIDO!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.04,0:14:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the base of the Undead Legion.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So Maam's down there?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.79,0:15:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The temple was empty,\Nso they probably took her down there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Then Crocodine...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He probably died.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It looked like his wounds\Nfrom fighting you hadn't fully healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That's strange.\NThe usual guards aren't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Then that's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.06,0:15:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.94,0:15:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.07,0:15:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,-Okay!\N-Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,With my mighty sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.57,0:15:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you don't have to, old timer!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,They called me\Nthe greatest swordsman in Papunica!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We need you here\Nto keep watch just in case!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.08,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We're off then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.21,0:15:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's better this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.46,0:15:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No offense to him, but that old man\Ncan't do anything against Hyunckel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.14,0:15:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:58.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with us.\NWe can't use Raiden underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.43,0:16:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we find Maam, we run. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel will be tough to beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.56,0:16:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Dai, I've been thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.36,0:16:09.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hyunckel is in the wrong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.11,0:16:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I get he has his motives...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,but that doesn't excuse\Ndestroying Papunica Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.24,0:16:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.08,0:16:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}when I fought him, I was terrified.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.83,0:16:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I thought of running away like that one time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.09,0:16:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But thinking about justice,\Nand Maam, and you made me feel
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.55,0:16:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,that I had to try no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.05,0:16:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,When that happened,\NI felt a little less scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so I come after Maam?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Come on! I'm being serious here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.94,0:16:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,If Hyunckel chases us outside,\Nthat's when we'll fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.20,0:16:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.28,0:16:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The brats have entered the palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead them to where\NMaster Hyunckel commanded!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.58,0:17:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.08,0:17:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh no!\NI've got to get out of here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,G-Gomechan?!\NWhen did you get in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.05,0:17:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you were worried about me\Nand snuck in.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.35,0:17:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.18,0:17:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gomechan, can you get those?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This place is huge.\NWe can't find the prison at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.44,0:17:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This used to be Hadorra's Dark Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.45,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Merami!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The hostage has escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.91,0:17:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.96,0:17:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's narrow, but hang in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an air duct,\Nso there has to be an exit.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.65,0:18:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There! An exit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.73,0:18:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the Colosseum\Nof the Underground Palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.66,0:18:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh crap! It's a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.62,0:18:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Dark Lord Hadorra used to have\Nprisoners fight monsters,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and he enjoyed watching\Nthe death in this bloody place.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.33,0:18:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I chose it as the perfect place for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already fully armoured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We can see the sky here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Your time to end has come!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Maam?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.18,0:18:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. Once you're dead,\NI'll have no use for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.73,0:18:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be safely released.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.77,0:18:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, you can leave as well, Mage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thanks but no thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.49,0:18:59.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, we'll have to fight here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's target him\Nwhen he raises his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.83,0:19:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need my sword!\NI'll crush you right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.31,0:19:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's toying with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.48,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He won't use his sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll draw his attention!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You summon the clouds!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.32,0:19:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.78,0:19:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.11,0:19:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you given up?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.62,0:19:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! Haven't you realized\Nyou're outmatched?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's anticipating my movements?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.63,0:20:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good going, Dai!\NJust hold on a little longer!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.93,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Spirits scattered in the heavens,\Nhear my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a hidden room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.28,0:20:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! A treasure chest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.41,0:20:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Sh-Should I open it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.96,0:20:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's a Cannibox.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But it could contain some useful,\Npowerful legendary weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.43,0:20:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-This is...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.23,0:20:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just one fight and he's already\Nkeeping up with me?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.98,0:20:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Chain Mail?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.16,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow, ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.\NIf it's a gruesome death you seek,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.08,0:21:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll end you with my blade of hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.00,0:21:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Here it is!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Time to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.17,0:21:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Popp, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.68,0:21:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Ranarion!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.31,0:21:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.77,0:21:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{\3c&H1717E4&}Raiden!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.66,0:21:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.12,0:21:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it! Hooray! Hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kindness is the magic of kind people{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:25.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}yasashisa wa yasashii hito ga tsukaeru mahou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Then do I have no choice\NBut to just be a normal person?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.15,0:22:32.99,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}jaa boku wa tada no hito de iru shikanaino?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm not sure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:36.21,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}doudarou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if the place I call home may change{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.50,0:22:44.17,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}kaeru basho wa ne kawatte yuku kedo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Listen to me, Mother{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.34,0:22:46.72,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}naa kaasan boku wa{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I will never change those I protect{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.88,0:22:52.85,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mamoru hito wo kaetari shinai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what you'd say{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.31,0:22:57.52,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}anata wa nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At times I can be cowardly and small{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.69,0:23:01.73,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}tokiyori yowaki de chippoke de{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What would you say to me\NAs I hesitate to even hesitate?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.90,0:23:08.20,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}mayou koto ni mo mayou boku ni nannte iukana{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Unlike the today that I sought{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.36,0:23:14.03,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sagashite ita kyou to chigatte{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure you'd laugh at my disappointment{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.20,0:23:19.33,On Top,,0,0,0,,{\i1}ochikonnde shimau boku wo warau no darou{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.10,0:23:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}With his anger towards justice,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.56,0:23:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hyunckel's power is overwhelming\Nin both sword and magic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.60,0:23:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Helpless, Dai falls prey\Nto his Bloody Sukuraido!{\i0}{\3c&H00000000&}.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.44,0:23:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All appears to be over, but Hyunckel\Nis shocked by a truth that Maam reveals.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.53,0:23:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just then, Dai rises again!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.03,0:23:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,DRAGON QUEST The Adventure of Dai{\i1},{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.49,0:23:57.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"The Deciding Moment"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.12,0:24:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The adventure continues!{\i0}
